title: Upgrading and Repairing PCs (21st Edition) EPUB
description:
English | 2013 | ISBN: 0789750007 | ISBN-13: 9780789750006 | 1200 pages | EPUB | 21,3 MB

For 25 years, Upgrading and Repairing PCs has been the worlds #1 guide to PC hardware: The single source for reliable information on troubleshooting and fixing problems, adding hardware, optimizing performance, and building new PCs. 

Now, better than ever, this 21st edition offers beefed-up coverage of the newest hardware innovations and maintenance techniques, plus more than two hours of new DVD video.
